 "": {
 "": {
 "": ""
 }
 },
 }
}
`

### Date histogram

- https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/8.4/search-aggregations-bucket-datehistogram-aggregation.html

`json
POST //_search
{
 "aggs": {
 "": {
